---
title: Hearty Veggie and Chorizo Chili with Tortilla Chips
description: Simple but fantastic, this delicious chili is filled with beans, chorizo, bell peppers and tomatoes. Each bite is tender and comforting. We suggest using the tortilla chips to scoop up and enjoy every last drop!
